<div class="nbunit" id="19Aug1938"><font color="red">19 August 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Harriet Weaver to Paul L&eacute;on): I have posted to Mr Joyce today the fourth piece I typed out for him when he was at Bognor &mdash; Tristan and Isolde. </div>
